Direct Known Subclasses:
ConstantFieldref, ConstantInterfaceMethodref, ConstantMethodref
public abstract class ConstantFieldInterfaceMethod
extends Constant

Abstract class, combining data of the class structures CONSTANT_Fieldref_info, CONSTANT_InterfaceMethodref_info and CONSTANT_Methodref_info. It is inherited by the concrete classes for these constants.

Version:
1.0.0, 2010-03-11
